SSV Staking contract
        |
        v
Distributed to cSSV holders

Oracle Delegation (v1)
When you stake SSV, your weight is automatically split equally across all 4 oracles. This simplified model ensures:

All stakers participate in oracle consensus
75% quorum required for commitments
No manual delegation needed
